{
  "texts": [
    "The findings from Table 4 indicate that the students' evaluations of ChatGPT had a moderate impact on \"perceived usefulness\" (0.46 > 0.40), \"perceived ease of use\" (0.55 > 0.50), and \"intention to use\" (0.65 > 0.50).",
    "According to our analysis, the \"perceived usefulness, perceived ease of use, and intention to use\" of ChatGPT among college students improved significantly after some time of usage.",
    "This finding suggests that students perceived ChatGPT as more practical, userfriendly, and inclined to utilize it again.",
    "Conversely, these enhancements failed to yield a favorable influence on their \"attitude towards utilization. \"",
    "This implies that while students were receptive to utilizing ChatGPT for practical purposes, the perceived benefits did not result in favorable emotional responses or supersede preexisting inclinations."
  ]
}